title: GTA V Update 5 Patch for RT GTA V
description:
As some of you may know, my 'GTA V' installer was missing update 5 (v1.0.350.2) - This patch will correct this!

Included in the setup:

* Official GTA V Update 5 (v1.0.350.2)

* Ill Gotten Gains 1 + 2

* Rockstar Social Club v1.1.6.1 (Necessary to play 'Ill Gotten Gains'


The 3DM no-CD ended up having less issues with crashing the game than Reloaded's did, so I included that in a ZIP file here ...
